<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 09:15:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国拖延季度销售后，欧莱雅股票下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-shares-drop-after-china-drags-down-quarterly-sales-2025-02-07/</link><description>法国化妆品巨头L&amp;#39;Oreal的股票在周五的早期交易中下跌了4％以上，此前该公司发布了自大流行以来最慢的季度销售，而中国的需求却拖累了。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 09:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-shares-drop-after-china-drags-down-quarterly-sales-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国副总理将参加巴黎AI峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-vice-premier-set-attend-paris-ai-summit-2025-02-07/</link><description>外交部周五表示，中国副总理张盖奎宁将于2月12日至2月12日在AI行动峰会上担任习近平总统的特别代表。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-vice-premier-set-attend-paris-ai-summit-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Shein准备在伦敦IPO上将估值削减至500亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-poised-slash-valuation-50-billion-london-ipo-sources-say-2025-02-07/</link><description>三名了解此事的人说，在线快速时尚零售商Shein将在伦敦的潜在上市中将其估值降低到约500亿美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-poised-slash-valuation-50-billion-london-ipo-sources-say-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>当汽车制造商警告新车型的成本时，保时捷与2025年的新型号的成本有所不同</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/luxury-carmaker-porsches-grim-2025-outlook-sends-shares-down-2025-02-07/</link><description>保时捷AG的股价在周五下降了7％，这是欧洲公司中最大的下跌，也是自股市上市以来最糟糕的一天，此前汽车制造商警告说，新车型和与电池相关的费用的成本将削弱其2025年利润。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:36:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/luxury-carmaker-porsches-grim-2025-outlook-sends-shares-down-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港向美国关税决定向世贸组织投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-complain-wto-us-tariff-decision-2025-02-07/</link><description>香港周五表示，将向世界贸易组织（WTO）提出投诉，要求美国决定对亚洲金融枢纽的商品征收10％的关税，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）以中国进口为目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-complain-wto-us-tariff-decision-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>雅芳（Avolon</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/avolon-settles-lawsuit-against-insurers-over-stranded-russian-jets-2025-02-07/</link><description>全球第二大飞机露西（Worth）在周五说，当西方制裁迫使2022年终止其租赁时，阿沃隆（Avolon）针对许多飞机的诉讼就被阻止了俄罗斯。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 07:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/avolon-settles-lawsuit-against-insurers-over-stranded-russian-jets-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>德国出口上升，工业生产下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-industrial-production-falls-2025-02-07/</link><description>德国出口在12月上升，而工业产出的下降超出了预期，这表明欧元区最大的经济体的前景仍然没有玫瑰色。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 07:22:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/german-exports-rise-industrial-production-falls-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国一月的银行贷款飙升，但需求仍然脆弱：路透社民意调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-bank-lending-seen-surging-demand-still-fragile-2025-02-07/</link><description>路透社的一项民意调查显示，与12月相比，中国的新人民币贷款可能在1月份飙升，但仍低于一年前的创纪录水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 06:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-bank-lending-seen-surging-demand-still-fragile-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗谴责与美国运输有关的新制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-condemns-new-us-shipping-related-sanctions-2025-02-07/</link><description>据官方IRNA通讯社报道，伊朗谴责华盛顿采取与运输相关的制裁的举动，称这将阻止其与合作伙伴的合法交易。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 06:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-condemns-new-us-shipping-related-sanctions-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在中国贸易战aimmers时会见日本的伊西邦</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-meets-japans-ishiba-china-trade-war-simmers-2025-02-07/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）将于周五首次与日本总理史密斯·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）会面，因为两个盟友对中国崛起的工作保持着谨慎的努力，以促进商业和安全关系，同时又有一场贸易战升级威胁着全球经济破裂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 06:04:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-meets-japans-ishiba-china-trade-war-simmers-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>晨价：中国AI拉力赛贸易战争市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-07/</link><description>看看Ankur Banejee的欧洲和全球市场的前一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 05:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>泰国领导人吸引中国游客，她说她“中国血液”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/wooing-chinese-tourists-thai-leader-says-she-has-chinese-blood-her-2025-02-07/</link><description>泰国总理寻求在访问泰国的中国游客中解决安全问题，他说她“中国血”，她亲自研究了安全方案，以确保中国公民的安全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 05:31:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/wooing-chinese-tourists-thai-leader-says-she-has-chinese-blood-her-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-explore-ways-ramp-up-auto-production-ceo-says-2025-02-07/</link><description>首席执行官兼创始人雷·朱（Lei Jun）周五在他的社交媒体帐户上说，中国小米将探索提高汽车生产能力的方法。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 02:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-explore-ways-ramp-up-auto-production-ceo-says-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普对中国咬人的关税在线购物者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trumps-tariffs-china-bite-us-bargain-hunting-online-shoppers-2025-02-06/</link><description>周三，马修·坎农（Matthew Cannon）的大学时代女儿向他转发了DHL的请求DHL的要求，要求与澳大利亚时尚销售商I.am.am.gia的订单相关的45.19美元费用。她想知道这是否是骗局。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 23:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/trumps-tariffs-china-bite-us-bargain-hunting-online-shoppers-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>晨价：印度眼睛的历史性降低，全球宽松势头安装</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2025-02-06/</link><description>看看亚洲市场的前一天。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphics-2025-02-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>